data.title: Minneapolis StarTribune
data.meta_description: Minneapolis StarTribune - a place for remembering loved ones; a space for sharing memories, life stories, milestones, to express condolences, and celebrate life of your loved ones
data.text:
Cathy Barker

Barker, Cathy A. 72, of Fridley passed away Aug. 16, 2024. Retired from U.S. Marshals Office. Preceded in death by parents Clifford & Doris Klemenhagen. Ruth Baune

Baune, Ruth Frieda April 18, 1936 - August 14, 2024 Age 88, of Brooklyn Park, MN, passed away on August 14, 2024. Beloved wife, mother, grandmother, and great-grandmother. Ruth was born in Schwerin Germany. At age 18 she was hired as a seamstress on a ship where she worked for 4 years. Her love of travel brought...

John Billingsley

John H. Billingsley, 84, of Owatonna, passed away on Saturday, August 17, 2024 at Allin Hospital of Faribault. John the son of Richard and Esther (Johnson) Billingsley was born on February 7, 1940 in Minneapolis. He graduated from Minneapolis Southwest High School, University of Minnesota and Mankato State College...

Eric DeTuncq

Eric James DeTuncq, 71, of St. Paul, passed away at home on August 4, 2024. He was born on August 11, 1952 to Ann and Wayne DeTuncq in Des Moines, Iowa and was raised in Minneapolis, Minnesota. Charlotte Egeberg

Egeberg, Charlotte Bernice (Forness) 96, formerly of St. Louis Park MN, died on Sunday, Aug. 18, 2024 at Cottage- wood Senior Communities in Rochester MN. Charlotte (Chuckie) was born on October 25, 1927, to Albert and Bertina Forness in Fargo ND. She was united in marriage to Herman Egeberg on July 1, 1950....

Roberta Hoffman

Hoffman, Roberta Davis Minnetonka, born June 28, 1948, passed away peacefully in her sleep on August 18th after several years of declining health and battling a rare form of Myositis. Kathleen Hubbard

Hubbard, Kathleen Ann "Kathy" May 29, 1945 - July 30, 2024 Kathy Hubbard left us much too soon on July 30, 2024. Her full obituary was published in the Star Tribune (August 4 and 5, 2024). A Celebration of Life will be held September 14, 2024, 2 pm at Pinstripes, 3849 Gallagher Drive, Edina, MN 55435. In...

Anne W. Grande

Anne W. Grande 8/17/2010 So much love. So little time. You live on in our hearts. Denis Peter, Emily, Gummy, Franny

Ingrid Erica White

Ingrid Erica White June 17, 1977 to August 12, 2014 Though you are no longer with us, you will never be forgotten.

Jan Boylan

Four years and still deeply missed "so much bad." Until we meet again mama, may you sing with the angels and continue to feel our love

Jill & Kelly

ELEANOR I. WALIOR

ELEANOR I. WALIOR Dec. 29, 1938 - Aug. 8, 2011 Forever in our hearts; your memories are treasured every day. Your husband, children, grandchildren, family and friends miss you

KEN "KENNY" CZUPTA

KEN "KENNY" CZUPTA Aug. 5, 1968 Aug. 20, 2006 Hi Ken, Tomorrow would be your 56th Birthday, August 5, 1968. You were actually born on a Monday. Wishing you a very Happy Birthday. Love, Love, Love You! Mom, David, Cindy, Family & Friends

Adam Engman-Delforge

Adam Engman-Delforge 8/4/80 - 3/28/03 "If I could turn back time, If I could find a way, If I could reach the stars, I'd give 'em all to you." I remember you every day, but especially on your birthday. Love you forever, Your Mother
